        <name>Start</name>
        <qualifiedname>Assets.Scripts.Scheduling.Validation.CrossValidator.Start</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="namespace_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_unity" kindref="compound">Unity</ref> lifecycle callback — runs the full export pipeline on scene start. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Performs the following steps in order:<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Creates <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_cross_validator_1a80ede1968dc597c505ef36ec96837d23" kindref="member">outputDirectory</ref> if it does not exist.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Validates that <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_cross_validator_1a874643c3bab4c70ffecb10fd871e963e" kindref="member">instanceDirectory</ref> exists; logs a <computeroutput>Debug.LogError</computeroutput> and aborts if not.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Logs the resolved paths for both directories.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Delegates to ValidationExporter.RunAndExport to simulate all instances and write output files.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Logs the <computeroutput><ref refid="compare__results_8py" kindref="compound">compare_results.py</ref></computeroutput> invocation command for convenience. </para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
