    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="namespace_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_unity" kindref="compound">Unity</ref> entry point that exports C# makespan results for cross-validation against job_shop_lib. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Attach to any GameObject in the scene. On Play, the component locates all Taillard JSON files in <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_cross_validator_1a874643c3bab4c70ffecb10fd871e963e" kindref="member">instanceDirectory</ref>, runs ValidationExporter.RunAndExport to simulate every instance under every DispatchingRule, and writes <computeroutput>csharp_makespans.csv</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>csharp_schedules.json</computeroutput> to <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_cross_validator_1a80ede1968dc597c505ef36ec96837d23" kindref="member">outputDirectory</ref>. The exported files are then consumed by <computeroutput><ref refid="compare__results_8py" kindref="compound">compare_results.py</ref></computeroutput> to diff C# results against the Python job_shop_lib reference.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Setup</title><para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Place Taillard JSON files in <computeroutput>Assets/Resources/Instances/</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Copy the same files to a regular folder (e.g. <computeroutput>Assets/StreamingAssets/Instances/</computeroutput>) because ValidationExporter reads directly from disk, not via <computeroutput>Resources.Load</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Set <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_cross_validator_1a874643c3bab4c70ffecb10fd871e963e" kindref="member">instanceDirectory</ref> and <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_cross_validator_1a80ede1968dc597c505ef36ec96837d23" kindref="member">outputDirectory</ref> in the Inspector.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Enter Play Mode.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Run <computeroutput><ref refid="compare__results_8py" kindref="compound">compare_results.py</ref></computeroutput> from the output directory: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">cd<sp/>Assets/StreamingAssets/Validation</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python<sp/>compare_results.py</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>This component does not use the <ref refid="namespace_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_unity" kindref="compound">Unity</ref> Resources system. Both directories must be accessible as real filesystem paths at runtime, not <ref refid="namespace_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_unity" kindref="compound">Unity</ref> virtual paths. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
